cars.description: This malodorous, rusted, and barely functional vehicle has ample mileage and a chronic oil-pan malady. But it runs!
Clearly a better choice than the Subaru legacy, this fully functional vehicle won't bleed you of twice its resale value at least every other month.
Your mom called and told us that if it was good enough for you when you were six, it's good enough for you now.
A real steal. No one's really sure why this car is so cheap, or so orange. Luckily for you, it's not in stock.
The to purchase when you are a competent and adequately compensated developer. Too bad you'll be so close to retirement.
Henry Ford was wrong: they also come in Seagreen.
